n三、依刑事訴訟法第451條第1項聲請逕以簡易判決處刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/110%2c%e6%9c%b4%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c38%2c20210204%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,110,朴交簡,38,20210204,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"朴交簡","JNO":"38","JDATE":"20210204","JTITLE":"公共危險"}